The Teladi Falcon is a well regarded fighter. Its excellent speed, paired with reasonable strength and weaponry, make it a popular choice for fighter pilots on a budget.\n\nThe Falcon Sentinel is thought by many to be a compromise too far, with reduced speed and increased resilience rendering the overall performance somewhat mediocre.
